pageProduct.name: Swisse Skincare Olive Leaf Deep Cleansing Gel 125ml
pageProduct.description:
General Information

SWISSE OLIVE LEAF DEEP CLEANSING GEL
effectively cleanses and removes makeup and impurities
without over-drying, leaving the skin feeling purified and
refreshed. Formulated with soothing Aloe Vera, it leaves
the skin clear, calm and hydrated.

Suitable For: Oily and combination skin

Size: 125mL

Warnings

Test prior to use. In the unlikely event of a negative reaction, consult your medical practitioner.

Ingredients

Aqua (Water)
ALOE VERA Aqueous Extract of Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf
Glycerin
Cocamidopropyl Betaine
Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate
Xanthan Gum
Sodium Glycolate
OLIVE LEAF Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Extract
Glycolic Acid
Hamamelis Virginiana Flower Water
Allantoin
Echinacea Angustifolia Extract
PLANTOLIN Centipeda Cunninghamii (Plantolin) Extract
GRAPEFRUIT Citrus Grandis (Grapefruit) Peel Oil
BERGAMOT Citrus Aurantium Bergamia (Bergamot) Fruit Oil
SANDALWOOD Fusanus Spicatus (Sandalwood) Wood Oil
CHAMOMILE Anthemis Nobilis Flower (Chamomile) Oil
Cedrus Atlantica Bark Oil
Passiflora Incarnata Extract
LINSEED Linum Usitatissimum (Linseed) Seed Oil
Vaccinium Myrtillus Fruit Extract
SUGAR CANE Saccharum Officinarum (Sugar Cane) Extract
ORANGE Citrus Aurantium Dulcis (Orange) Fruit Extract
LEMON Citrus Medica Limonum (Lemon) Fruit Extract
SUGAR MAPLE Acer Saccharum (Sugar Maple) Extract
Salicylic Acid
Sodium Citrate
Benzyl Alcohol
Dehydroacetic Acid

Directions

Blend a small amount between palms
and massage into wet skin in a circular motion. Rinse
with warm water. Recommended for use twice daily, in the morning and evening.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 28°C.
